<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>io.github.nostar.DroidStar</id>
  <name>DroidStar</name>
  <summary>A D-Star client for PC</summary>
  <description>
    <p>DroidStar is an application that allows you to use the digital mode D-Star from a computer.
      It connects to a reflector server and sends and receives audio encoded in AMBE. It also
      displays information about the users and modules connected to the reflector.</p>
  </description>
